1
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:31,599
When has this old minister ever associated with you two?

2
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:35,799
Where does this talk of collusion come from?

3
00:01:36,359 --> 00:01:37,599
Is that truly the case?

4
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:41,439
Do you actually have solid evidence?

5
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,079
Your guilty servant did indeed

6
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:47,920
exchange letters with Steward Ding of the Left Chancellor's residence.

7
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,719
But I was merely following orders.

8
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,400
But I never imagined this.

9
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:54,760
How could your guilty servant dare
embezzle the gold mine?

10
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,400
It was Ma Kaicheng who said

11
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,920
the orders came from the Left Chancellor.

12
00:01:58,159 --> 00:02:00,519
Your guilty servant was only
carrying out duties as usual.

13
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,560
Your Majesty.

14
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:04,400
Whatever Ma Kaicheng says becomes truth?

15
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:06,239
Do you not use your head at all?

16
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,400
To pin baseless accusations

17
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:11,159
upon this old man's head,

18
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:14,360
what are your true intentions?

19
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,159
Your Majesty.

20
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,879
Steward Ding of the Left Chancellor's
residence has committed treason.

21
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,000
This old minister failed
to discipline him strictly.

22
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,719
I am guilty of negligence.

23
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:31,639
This old minister wishes to resign
and return home.

24
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:34,000
I beg Your Majesty to grant permission.

25
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,039
Your Majesty.

26
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,520
The Left Chancellor handles
countless affairs daily.

27
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,680
Some oversights are unavoidable.

28
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,000
Please show mercy, Your Majesty.

29
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,599
Your Majesty.

30
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,400
The Left Chancellor
has rendered great service.

31
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,319
If, for this minor charge of negligence,

32
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,960
he is dismissed from office,

33
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,400
this minister deems it improper.

34
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,039
This minister concurs.

35
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,639
This minister concurs.

36
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,520
This minister concurs.

37
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:05,400
The Left Chancellor cannot be
touched right now.

38
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:24,319
I have served as Chancellor for decades.

39
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,599
You think a bastard like you

40
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,280
can bring me down?

41
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,240
An ant trying to shake a great tree.

42
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,360
Utterly laughable.

43
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,639
Cunning old fox.

44
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:38,520
Ning Chen.

45
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,479
What about Ma Kaicheng?

46
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,039
Where is he now?

47
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,879
You want solid evidence, is that it?

48
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,240
I will give it to you.

49
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,920
You have grown up.

50
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:33,120
But you still act too rashly.

51
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:34,959
No matter.

52
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:38,959
Father shall make this final move for you.

53
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,560
Ning Ziming, have you gone mad?

54
00:04:43,959 --> 00:04:44,879
Yes, I have gone mad.

55
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,800
Ever since the death of Ning Chen's mother,

56
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:47,720
I have been mad.

57
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:50,360
I have waited for this day

58
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:53,480
for far too long.

59
00:04:54,199 --> 00:04:55,680
Alone, I could not bring you down.

60
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:57,399
But now my son has come of age.

61
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,279
I have nothing left to fear.

62
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,279
Your Majesty,

63
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,000
this minister can bear witness.

64
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:07,000
Every word they have spoken is true.

65
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:09,879
The Left Chancellor's crimes
are too many to record.

66
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:11,079
This minister has proof.

67
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,399
I beg Your Majesty's permission
to present it.

68
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,720
Granted.

69
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,959
Summon him.

70
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,279
Reporting to Your Majesty,

71
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,000
this man is Ma Kaicheng.

72
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,519
Your Majesty,

73
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,079
this guilty commoner,
on the Left Chancellor's order,

74
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,759
joined with Zhang Yuancang

75
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:36,639
to mine gold ore.

76
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,759
And as for Ning Chen's mother,

77
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,439
she discovered the gold mine

78
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:41,800
and reported it to the court.

79
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:45,160
To cover up the truth,
the Left Chancellor

80
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:48,560
ordered this guilty man to poison her.

81
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:49,920
Silence!

82
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:52,120
You beast!

83
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:54,199
This old minister bears you no grudge.

84
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,279
Why do you slander me?

85
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,240
No grudge, you say?

86
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,399
Lord Left Chancellor,

87
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,240
if Minister Ning had not

88
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,639
spirited me and my family away in time,

89
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,199
I fear

90
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:06,720
my entire family

91
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,680
would have long since fallen by your hand.

92
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:10,240
Is there hard evidence?

93
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,160
The evidence is here.

94
00:06:17,959 --> 00:06:18,920
In the fourth year of Rende,

95
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,879
Bingzhou suffered great drought,
with no harvest at all.

96
00:06:22,319 --> 00:06:24,120
The Left Chancellor seized the lands

97
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,519
and embezzled seventy percent
of the relief funds,

98
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,800
leaving Bingzhou strewn with the starved.

99
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,439
The people were driven to revolt,

100
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,360
and he then sent troops to suppress them,

101
00:06:33,399 --> 00:06:36,120
killing and wounding civilians
by the tens of thousands.

102
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:38,879
In the sixth year of Rende,

103
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:41,720
the Left Chancellor secretly received
ten beauties from Tuoluo,

104
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,000
along with five hundred thousand
taels of gold,

105
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,319
and in return delivered
our border defense maps,

106
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,800
causing our frontier army to suffer defeat,

107
00:06:49,759 --> 00:06:50,759
with losses among our soldiers

108
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,839
exceeding twenty thousand.

109
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:54,680
In the ninth year of Rende,

110
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,519
the Left Chancellor secretly
administered poison,

111
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:59,040
causing the sudden death of
the Second Prince of Great Xuan.

112
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,639
Afterwards, he sent men

113
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:03,680
to remove the tea set
the Second Prince had used,

114
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,720
to conceal the truth.

115
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,240
Ning Ziming,

116
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:19,759
why did you not report this in time?

117
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,199
Your guilty servant
acknowledges his crime.

118
00:07:23,319 --> 00:07:25,040
Ning Ziming,

119
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,839
do you know what you are doing?

120
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,920
Of all the matters you just laid out,

121
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,560
which one did you not have a hand in?

122
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,800
Do you intend to drag the entire
Ning family down with you?

123
00:07:37,879 --> 00:07:40,519
Have you no thought for
your wife and children?

124
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:42,560
Your Majesty,

125
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:44,160
the evidence presented here

126
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:46,560
suffices to prove the Left Chancellor's
manifold crimes.

127
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,160
This minister, too, is implicated.

128
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,120
I beg for nothing else,

129
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,839
only that Your Majesty,

130
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:54,399
in light of this minister's service
in bringing forth this evidence,

131
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:58,399
spare my second and third sons.

132
00:07:59,519 --> 00:08:00,920
They knew nothing of any of this.

133
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,759
They are truly innocent.

134
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,680
Chang Suoxiang.

135
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:23,800
All these years We placed such trust in you,

136
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,759
elevating you step by step
to head all officials.

137
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,600
And yet you...

138
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:30,240
Is this how you repay Us?

139
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:32,039
Your Majesty.

140
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:35,519
Guards!

141
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,039
Throw this cur

142
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:43,240
into the imperial dungeon at once.

143
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,240
Yes, Your Majesty.

144
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,679
Geng Jing.

145
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,759
Your servant is here.

146
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:48,720
Seize and search
the Chancellor's residence.

147
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,960
All persons involved are to be
cast into the death cells.

148
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,919
Should anyone dare obstruct or resist,

149
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:57,080
strike off their heads,

150
00:08:57,759 --> 00:09:00,600
one by one, in Our name.

151
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,559
Your servant obeys the decree.

152
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,120
Your Majesty.

153
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:07,559
In the case of Zhang Yuancang, Ning Chen

154
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:09,639
committed the crime of
deceiving the sovereign.

155
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:17,240
We nearly forgot about you.

156
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,320
Minister Yu,

157
00:09:20,039 --> 00:09:21,039
in the case of the Left Chancellor,

158
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,159
you covered for him at every turn.

159
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,159
Yet in the matter of Ning Chen,

160
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,799
you pressed harder at every step.

161
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:28,480
You...

162
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:32,639
Do you truly take Us for a fool?

163
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,000
Take him away.

164
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,759
Subject him to severe interrogation,

165
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,879
and await Our judgment.

166
00:09:38,919 --> 00:09:39,440
Yes, Your Majesty.

167
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,480
Your Majesty is wise and just.

168
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,120
Court is dismissed.

169
00:09:47,639 --> 00:09:51,759
Long live Your Majesty, ten thousand years!

170
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,360
Why have you come?

171
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:23,000
At a time like this,

172
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,799
should you not be cutting ties with me?

173
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:27,759
I came seeking an answer.

174
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:35,279
If not for your military merits,

175
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,240
I think for the rest of my life,

176
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,320
I would never have brought out
this evidence.

177
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,600
Now,

178
00:10:41,519 --> 00:10:42,960
you are capable of protecting yourself.

179
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,960
One last move would checkmate
the Left Chancellor.

180
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:49,320
How could Father stand idle

181
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,639
and watch you fail?

182
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,399
I know

183
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:57,039
I have wronged your mother,

184
00:10:57,759 --> 00:10:58,600
and wronged you as well.

185
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,360
Back then, when your mother and I

186
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,200
secretly pledged ourselves to each other,

187
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,639
I promised

188
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:05,559
that once I passed the imperial exams,

189
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:07,080
I would return and take her as my wife.

190
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,720
Who would have thought,
when the results were posted,

191
00:11:10,559 --> 00:11:12,399
Chang Ruyue had set her sights on me.

192
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,879
She used your mother to threaten me.

193
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,799
But back then I was merely a scholar,

194
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:23,120
and she was the Left Chancellor's
daughter.

195
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:26,399
I truly had no choice.

196
00:11:28,519 --> 00:11:29,440
But I do not understand.

197
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,480
If you feared the Left Chancellor so,

198
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,279
why did you bring me back
to the Ning residence?

199
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,799
And when did you

200
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:41,639
begin gathering evidence
of the Left Chancellor's crimes?

201
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,799
After what happened to your mother,

202
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:45,519
I guessed that Chang Ruyue

203
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,159
would surely seek to root out all traces.

204
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:48,919
With you staying at the Ning residence,

205
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,600
they would be constrained by appearances.

206
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:52,759
Even if they mistreated you,

207
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:54,679
at least your life would be preserved.

208
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:57,799
From that moment, I swore

209
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,480
I would bring down the Left Chancellor.

210
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,240
Because as long as he lived,

211
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:06,200
you would always be in danger.

212
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:09,960
And what of Ma Kaicheng?

213
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:12,759
When I learned you had captured
Zhang Yuancang alive,

214
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,879
I knew the time had come.

215
00:12:19,799 --> 00:12:20,720
As your son,

216
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:23,399
I have no right to condemn your actions.

217
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:27,720
But neither do I have the standing

218
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:30,320
to forgive you on behalf of my mother.

219
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,320
Rest assured,

220
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:36,320
when I reach the underworld,

221
00:12:36,960 --> 00:12:38,639
I shall apologize to your mother myself.

222
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,519
But I would like

223
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,039
to ask one thing of you.

224
00:12:46,159 --> 00:12:47,039
Ning Xing and Ning Mao,

225
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,720
though they do not share your mother,

226
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,480
in the end,

227
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,879
you are all my children.

228
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,120
They are dull-witted,

229
00:12:56,799 --> 00:12:58,200
and pose no threat to you.

230
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,559
Even if you drive them out of the capital,

231
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,200
just spare their lives.

232
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,639
What about Ning Gan?

233
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,559
Was he not your most prized son?

234
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,519
He is not my blood at all.

235
00:13:15,279 --> 00:13:16,720
When Chang Ruyue first set
her eyes on me,

236
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,960
she had already conceived secretly

237
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:20,840
with a retainer of the chancellor's house.

238
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:22,759
That is why she was in such haste.

239
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:29,759
I shall try my best.

240
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,679
I am asking much of you.

241
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:41,240
Chen'er,

242
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,840
behind the Left Chancellor,

243
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:45,879
there is an even greater power.

244
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:49,960
What do you mean?

245
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,440
I cannot be certain myself.

246
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,559
I have always felt

247
00:13:54,279 --> 00:13:55,320
that the Left Chancellor alone

248
00:13:55,519 --> 00:13:57,000
could hardly stir up such great turmoil.

249
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:58,960
They have hidden themselves well.

250
00:13:59,399 --> 00:14:00,639
I have never managed to find proof.

251
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,960
Now that you have toppled
the Left Chancellor,

252
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:05,799
those behind him will surely make a move.

253
00:14:06,279 --> 00:14:07,039
So you,

254
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,840
you must take great care.

255
00:14:15,559 --> 00:14:16,120
Understood.

256
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:37,960
You have grown up.

257
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:39,960
Father can depart this world
with peace of mind.

258
00:15:08,879 --> 00:15:10,039
Father,

259
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:22,679
please accept your son's bow.

260
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,600
Take care.

